query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `drops` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `artistName` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `title` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `slug` varchar(255),
  `description` text,
  `editionSize` int NOT NULL,
  `dropStatus` enum('draft','published','archived') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'draft',
  `chapter` varchar(64),
  `storyBlurb` text,
  `priceIdr` int,
  `heroImageUrl` varchar(512),
  `productImages` text,
  `availableSizes` text,
  `keyTerms` text,
  `tags` text,
  `clearanceRequired` enum('none','initiate','member','inner_circle') DEFAULT 'none',
  `saleWindowStart` timestamp,
  `saleWindowEnd` timestamp,
  `visibilityLevel` enum('public','members','inner_circle') DEFAULT 'public',
  `publishedAt` timestamp,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `drops_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
